item.title: PEI-go-round with Xeon Kayak Ergometer
item.description: This is not the actual trip. This is just training mapped on chart to have an idea of what the real thing might be. April 9, 2023, lap2 16 days on ergo, 183 nautical miles, 340 km, lap2 Stats March 10, 2023, lap1 33 days on ergo, 281 nautical miles, 522 km, lap 1 Stats Xeon is a heavy-use Kayak Ergometer, that gives a true feel of on-the-water paddling.
